snippet.title: King of the Dwarves - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add King of the Dwarves to your Wishlist on Steam! 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/792610/King_of_the_Dwarves_Underground_City_Builder/

About the game:
Build an epic kingdom inside a mountain in this underground city builder. Mine and build in a vast procedurally generated 3D world. Gather resources, research technology, train warriors and engineers, forge weapons, fight monsters and manage hundreds of units. Become the King of the Dwarves! 

Follow Games Operators:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/franchise/gameops
Twitter - https://twitter.com/GamesOperators
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/GamesOperators/
